2. How we disclose your personal information
2.1 How this personal information will be used
The purpose of collecting personal information is to provide you with products and/or services and to ensure that we comply with applicable laws. You hereby consent to our processing of personal information for the purposes set out in this Privacy Policy and the disclosure of personal information to our affiliates (who are involved in communications, social media, technology and cloud businesses), third-party service providers (defined below).
We may use your personal information for the following purposes:
(a) Calculate athletic and health outcomes. We will use personal body data and/or data recorded by the device to calculate exercise and health results for display to you in the APP and/or device
(b) Physical condition analysis. Based on the personal physical data you provide and the data recorded by the device, we provide you with analysis related to your physical condition for your reference. For example: provide you with an ideal weight range for your reference; show you your current and/or whole-day stress value and/or stress change trend.
(c) Provide app services. After the relevant device is synchronized with the app, the data recorded in the device will be synchronized to the app and displayed to the user.
(d) Display caller information. When you receive an incoming call or text message, some devices that support this feature will display the data of the incoming call or message.
(e) Display music information. When you use the music control function, some devices that support this function will display music information (eg song title, song playback status, volume).
(h) Determine if the phone is supported. Information about your phone will be used to determine whether your phone can use the app.
(g) Provide alarm clock reminder function: We will collect your mobile phone alarm clock information, and when you turn on the mobile phone alarm clock reminder, we will remind you through the vibration of the device in time.
(h) Bluetooth camera: You can control the camera with your phone through some devices that support this function. To this end, the device will be paired with the mobile phone via Bluetooth to control taking pictures, and during the Bluetooth pairing process, it will also apply for the Bluetooth permission of the mobile phone.
(i) Provide women's health functions: when you choose to use women's health functions, you can record and view information related to menstrual periods on some devices or apps that support this function; we will predict your menstruation for you based on the information you fill in period and remind. We may also recommend suitable training courses for you based on the time of your menstrual period and your physical condition during menstruation.
(j) Displaying sleep information: We will use your personal body information and the data recorded by the device to calculate and analyze your sleep situation, which will be used to show you in the app, such as sleep score, sleep time, rapid eye movement sleep stage (REM), Distribution of sleep duration and sleep breathing quality.
(k) Provide network related services. Based on different network types, network signals and other information, the app will prompt the user about the traffic required to download sports-related videos, and determine whether there is a new version of the app that can be updated.
(l) Statistical analysis: We will conduct statistical analysis on our services or equipment, and may share these statistical data with the public or third parties to display the usage trends of our products or services, optimize products and services, Show you rankings, friend PK, etc., for example, by counting your steps, showing you results that are relevant to you (such as users in the same region), but these statistics do not contain any of your identification information.
3. Your rights to personal information
3.1 In order to make it easier for you to access, correct and delete your personal information during the use of the "FitCloudPro" application, and to ensure that you have the right to withdraw the right to use your personal information, we have provided you with corresponding operation settings in the product design , you can refer to the following guidelines to operate.
(a) Access. After installing and logging into "FitCloudPro", your personal information saved on the cloud will be automatically downloaded and synchronized to the local phone. In the "FitCloudPro" app, you can access your exercise data and health data through data cards, including step cards and exercise cards. You can view nickname, avatar, gender, date of birth, height, weight, and exercise settings data on the My page.
(b) Right to Correction. You can modify and update your nickname, avatar, gender, date of birth, height, weight, and exercise settings data on the "My" page, but for the accuracy and authority of the data, the data obtained automatically from your mobile phone or sports health device Data, does not provide editing and updating functions.
(c) After you stop using certain functions of "FitCloudPro", we will stop collecting your personal information related to the functions. We will delete or anonymize your personal information immediately after you delete your account.
(d) Account cancellation reminder. Please keep in mind that canceling an account is an unrecoverable operation. Before operating, please confirm that all data related to the account has been properly handled. If you cancel your account, you will not be able to use the account to retrieve all your exercise data or health records (even if you use the same mobile phone number or email to register), including but not limited to: you will not be able to log in and use the account ID. Your relatives and friends cannot add you as relatives and friends through this account ID; the health records, sleep records and exercise records under your account will not be retrieved; third-party sports health APPs (Apple Health, Google fit or WeChat Sports) associated with your account will not be retrieved ) will not be updated.
3.2 If you have any questions or suggestions, please contact us by sending an email to suggestions@topstep-tech.com(Huang Xin).
